graph LR
    MLflowOp[MLflow Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    MLflowOp -->|core service| MLflow[MLflow 2.x]
    MLflowOp -->|template engine| Helm[Helm 3.x<br/>embedded]

    %% External Dependencies (Database - one required)
    MLflowOp -->|prod database| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL 12+]
    MLflowOp -->|alt database| MySQL[MySQL]
    MLflowOp -->|dev database| SQLite[SQLite 3.x]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    MLflowOp -->|artifact storage| S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>MinIO/AWS S3]
    MLflowOp -->|TLS certs| ServiceCA[OpenShift service-ca]

    %% Kubernetes Platform
    MLflowOp -->|orchestration| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]
    MLflowOp -->|ingress| GatewayAPI[Gateway API<br/>HTTPRoute]
    MLflowOp -->|console integration| OpenShiftConsole[OpenShift Console<br/>ConsoleLink]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies (Integration Points)
    Notebooks[Notebooks/Workbenches] -->|experiment tracking| MLflowOp
    DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -->|pipeline metrics| MLflowOp
    TrainingOp[Training Operator] -->|training tracking| MLflowOp
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI management| MLflowOp

    %% Alternative/Overlapping
    MLflowOp -.->|alternative to| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]

    %% Monitoring
    MLflowOp -->|metrics export| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>ServiceMonitor]

    %% Storage
    MLflowOp -->|persistent volumes| PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim]

    %% Network Security
    MLflowOp -->|network policies| NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy<br/>egress/ingress]

